text.tspan: anchored position is position relative to virtual projection
of pivot of OffsetRT to AnchorsRect.
Anchor pivot is calculated by relations:
o1/o2 = a1/a2. SO it is calculated from OffsetRectPivot relative to anchor rect
Or even Anchor pivot is NormalPivot * AnchorRect.: 0.5 * anchor width;
Orange AnchorRectPivot is always set relative to OffsetRectPivot.
